channel.description:
[center][u][b][size=36pt]Z-Scape 585[/size][/b][/u][/center] [center][size=18pt][u][b]Zeta Games Ltd.[/b][/u][/size][/center]
[u][b][size=18pt]Sneak Peak Video[/size][/b][/u]: [size=18pt][b]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P8svpT317TQ[/b][/size]
Z-Scape 585 is an amazing server that has been in development for a while now. We are currently making a site and focusing extremely hard on stability. We hope to be online 24/7 with the help of the Z-Scape 585 community. Once the server is online be sure to try out the server! I guarantee you will love it.
Features: [u][b]Mini Games[/b][/u] Duel Arena Fight Pits Pest Control
[u][b]Skills[/b][/u] Atk Str Def Prayer Mage Range Herblore Thieving Craftign Rune Crafting Dungeoneering Summoning Slayer Construction Fletching Constitution Agility Hunter Mining Smithing Fishing Cooking Fire Making Wood Cutting Farming
[u][b]Special[/b][/u] GodWars Barrows Kalphite Queen KBD
[u][b]Miscellaneous[/b][/u] Grand Exchange Shops PVP PVNpc Auto Cast Music Quests Emotes Walking Running
More to come!
[u][b][size=18pt]Sneak Peak Video[/size][/b][/u]: [size=18pt][b]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P8svpT317TQ[/b][/size]
